Bilfinger to Name Foenss Schroeder to Board, Handelsblatt Says

-- B y   S h e e n a g h   M a t t h e w s
-- 
2011-03-18T08:13:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-18/bilfinger-to-name-foenss-schroeder-to-board-handelsblatt-says.html
  Bilfinger Berger SE (GBF)  and  Heidelberger Druckmaschinen AG (HDD)  plan to name Lone Foenss Schroeder to their supervisory boards,  Handelsblatt reported ,
citing unidentified people at the German companies.  Foenss Schroeder, a Danish lawyer and economist, will
become the only woman and only non-German representing
shareholders on Bilfinger and Heidelberger’s boards, the German
newspaper said.  Foenss Schroeder, former chief executive officer of  Sweden ’s Wallenius Lines AB, holds posts on the supervisory
boards of Swedish bank Svenska Handelsbanken AB and utility
Vattenfall AB, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sheenagh Matthews in Frankfurt at 
 smatthews6@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at   bkammel@bloomberg.net . 